We would expect to see such where there is a high incidence of previous exposure , and this , indeed , to be what in South . The good news is that its unlikely to suddenly stop all acquired immunity to disappear , but it will gradually degrade it . We are going to be a game of virus variant Whack - a - Mole for , and that is possibly an answer to those that question why the ordered , or for enough vaccine to give everybody in the 6 as , presumably the later can be to encompass more . The Institute specifically chose a , rather than human for the vector as it was unlikely their would be any significant resistance to it in the human population . However , it might be that , if are subject to repeated of the vector , then immunity to that will make it a lot less effective over time .
